Code preview of the table Country_Capital

USE DATABASECOUNTRYHL
go

IF EXISTS (SELECT 1
FROM SYS.SYSREFERENCES R JOIN SYS.SYSOBJECTS O ON (O.ID = R.CONSTID AND O.TYPE = 'F')
WHERE R.FKEYID = OBJECT_ID('COUNTRY_CAPITAL') AND O.NAME = 'FK_COUNTRY__COUNTRYCA_COUNTRY')
ALTER TABLE COUNTRY_CAPITAL
DROP CONSTRAINT FK_COUNTRY__COUNTRYCA_COUNTRY
go

IF EXISTS (SELECT 1
FROM SYSINDEXES
WHERE ID = OBJECT_ID('COUNTRY_CAPITAL')
AND NAME = 'COUNTRYCAPITAL_FK'
AND INDID > 0
AND INDID < 255)
DROP INDEX COUNTRY_CAPITAL.COUNTRYCAPITAL_FK
go

ALTER TABLE COUNTRY_CAPITAL
DROP CONSTRAINT PK_COUNTRY_CAPITAL
go

IF EXISTS (SELECT 1
FROM SYSOBJECTS
WHERE ID = OBJECT_ID('COUNTRY_CAPITAL')
AND TYPE = 'U')
DROP TABLE COUNTRY_CAPITAL
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: COUNTRY_CAPITAL */
/*==============================================================*/
CREATE TABLE COUNTRY_CAPITAL (
CCA_ID INT IDENTITY,
COU_ID INT NOT NULL,
CCA_NAME VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL
)
go

ALTER TABLE COUNTRY_CAPITAL
ADD CONSTRAINT PK_COUNTRY_CAPITAL PRIMARY KEY (CCA_ID)
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: COUNTRYCAPITAL_FK */
/*==============================================================*/




CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX COUNTRYCAPITAL_FK ON COUNTRY_CAPITAL (COU_ID ASC)
go

ALTER TABLE COUNTRY_CAPITAL
ADD CONSTRAINT FK_COUNTRY__COUNTRYCA_COUNTRY FOREIGN KEY (COU_ID)
REFERENCES COUNTRY (COU_ID)
go
